description:
Kafka.DotNet.InsideOut is a client API for producing and consuming kafka topics and ksqlDB push queries and views. 
    Targets .NET 5, .NET Core 3.1 and .NET Standard 2.0.
    Documentation for the library can be found at https://github.com/tomasfabian/Kafka.DotNet.ksqlDB/blob/main/Kafka.DotNet.InsideOut/Wiki.md.
title: Kafka.DotNet.InsideOut
